f522224e-65bb-4277-964b-c3d23583082d.title: Gadrin
f522224e-65bb-4277-964b-c3d23583082d.text:
Welcome to the Mining Guild.
My name's Gadrin and I'm the Guildmaster.
Can I help you with anything?

options.text: What have you got in the guild?
What do you dwarves do with the ore you mine?
Can you tell me about your skillcape?

5b467023-a592-4ac0-bab7-502d748ec79e.title: <player>
5b467023-a592-4ac0-bab7-502d748ec79e.text: What do you dwarves do with the ore you mine?

803dd679-e622-468d-ad18-56d52638f428.title: <player>
803dd679-e622-468d-ad18-56d52638f428.text: Can you tell me about your skillcape?

53ea917e-9fef-4a7d-9af2-cdedaf88a153.title: <player>
53ea917e-9fef-4a7d-9af2-cdedaf88a153.text: What have you got in the guild?

8ce42e16-b0ac-4476-a271-cbc5fa1999f2.title: Gadrin
8ce42e16-b0ac-4476-a271-cbc5fa1999f2.text:
All sorts of things!
There's plenty of coal rocks along with some iron,
mithril and adamantite as well.

38d03d96-cf14-4808-bc08-8c626dfba6dd.title: Gadrin
38d03d96-cf14-4808-bc08-8c626dfba6dd.text: There's no better mining site anywhere!

options.text: What do you dwarves do with the ore you mine?

34ff9734-5bfd-43e4-b907-b77042081171.title: Gadrin
34ff9734-5bfd-43e4-b907-b77042081171.text:
What do you think? We smelt it into bars, smith the
metal to make armour and weapons, then we exchange
them for goods and services.

87fe06be-db23-49b8-b509-df52c117cd53.title: <player>
87fe06be-db23-49b8-b509-df52c117cd53.text:
I don't see many dwarves
selling armour or weapons here.

149b4ea2-27a1-4c5c-8f12-f61be438f4f7.title: Gadrin
149b4ea2-27a1-4c5c-8f12-f61be438f4f7.text:
No, this is only a mining outpost. We dwarves don't
much like to settle in human cities. Most of the ore is
carted off to Keldagrim, the great dwarven city.
They've got a special blast furnace up there - it makes

5e9d1288-66af-496b-be9e-2c2b298625de.title: Gadrin
5e9d1288-66af-496b-be9e-2c2b298625de.text:
smelting the ore so much easier. There are plenty of
dwarven traders working in Keldagrim. Anyway, can I
help you with anything else?

options.text: What have you got in the guild?

321664bc-2dfd-4716-a78b-57ec1e5d6405.title: Gadrin
321664bc-2dfd-4716-a78b-57ec1e5d6405.text:
Sure, this is a Skillcape of Mining. It shows my stature
as a master miner! It has all sorts of uses including a
skill boost to my Mining skill and a chance of mining
extra ores. When you get to level 99 come and talk to

7ab040e9-537b-4f6c-84f3-3e8048a3d90b.title: Gadrin
7ab040e9-537b-4f6c-84f3-3e8048a3d90b.text: me and I'll sell you one.

9e27dac9-1ebc-4ccc-aba7-e11150ed894a.title: Gadrin
9e27dac9-1ebc-4ccc-aba7-e11150ed894a.text: Is there anything else I can help you with?

options.text: What have you got in the guild?
What do you dwarves do with the ore you mine?
